metadata.name: #1 Secret of the Subconscious
metadata.description:
The black and white artwork is 3300x4200 pixels
300 DPI

This artwork was created at night during my panic attack. The art is my therapy at this moment and it helps me to understand my subconscious, calm down and live all my emotions and experiences.

Sometimes it's understandable but our subconscious is a huge secret and no one of us know what it hides...
